## Package-Specific Checks

### Pre-Commit Quick Commands

```bash
# Build and check
R CMD build .
R CMD check {{PACKAGE_NAME}}_*.tar.gz

# Documentation
R -e "roxygen2::roxygenize()"

# Tests
R -e "devtools::test()"
```

